Don't miss this unique opportunity coming to St George, UT for 4 nights only. "Miss Saigon- In Concert" features an all star cast with James Royce Edwards, Brodie Perry, Alexa Garcia, Joel Thomas, Jake Thomas, Emme Condie, Cathy Ford and many , many more.

See it now or you will have to wait until it goes to Broadway in 2017. The "Rights" are no longer available in the U.S.A. Tickets are on sale at www.thestagedoortheater.com or www.showtix4u.com